              <strong>G</strong>: Toggle grid<br>
              <strong>Ctrl+Z</strong>: Undo<br>
              <strong>Ctrl+Y</strong>: Redo<br>
              <strong>Ctrl+0</strong>: Reset all
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

